jobInfo.postDescription:
上海site有5个研发的position，具体要求和jd可以私聊沟通，2-5年和5-8年的都有

ROLE INFORMATION:

As a developer, you will be working with Architects, Product managers and senior developers to deliver key enhancements and features in the SAP product.
You shall be part of an agile development team.  Design, Develop, test HCM Cloud applications using best coding standards and target architecture.  
Thinking in terms of High Availability, Scalability, Resiliency and Maintainability of Customer facing applications
Help develop test plans and also write Unit tests wherever needed.  
Testing automation is also required. Always with ‘Quality First’ mindset

EXPERIENCE:

2-5 years of experience in developing web-based applications.
knowledge of Computer Science fundamentals such as Object-Oriented Design Principles, Data Structures, Database, Operating Systems
Knowledge of scrum processes, passion for unit testing, integration testing and test automation.
Experience writing production quality code
Experience in developing and deploying applications using microservices would be a plus.
Experience working with Git 
Outstanding verbal and written communication skills.

Work Life Balance 10-6-5，15天年假，3%房补，过节红包，员工购股优惠，每年普调
jobInfo.address: 上海浦东新区SAP Labs China1号

brandComInfo.introduce: SAP公司（纽交所代码：SAP）成立于1972年，总部位于德国沃尔多夫市，在全球拥有6万多名员工，遍布全球130个国家，并拥有覆盖全球11,500家企业的合作伙伴网络。作为全球领先的企业管理软件解决方案提供商，SAP帮助各行业不同规模的企业实现卓越运营。从企业后台到公司决策层、从工厂仓库到商铺店面、从电脑桌面到移动终端—SAP助力用户和企业高效协作，获取商业洞见，并从竞争中脱颖而出。SAP的软件和服务能够帮助客户实现盈利性的运营，不断提升应变能力，实现可持续的增长。全球188个国家的232,000家客户正在从SAP解决方案中获益, 其中包括财富500强80%的企业及85%最有价值的品牌。
